#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties"
msgstr "Propriétés"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This button (only enabled for programs &ie; Desktop files) allows you to "
#| "change the properties of the program or script. You have general "
#| "properties, permissions properties, a preview when applicable and "
#| "properties related to the application for programs."
msgid ""
"This button is only shown when you hover the item with the mouse pointer. "
"The button (only enabled for programs and login scripts &ie; <filename class="
"\"extension\">.desktop</filename> files) allows you to change the properties "
"of the program or script. You have general properties, permissions "
"properties, a preview when applicable, and properties related to the "
"application or login script. The default command is extracted from the "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.desktop</filename> file from the "
"<literal>Exec</literal> key."
msgstr ""
"Ce bouton (activé uniquement pour lis programmes, &cad; les fichiers "
"Desktop) vous permet de modifier les propriétés du programme ou du script. "
"Vous avez les propriétés générales, les droits d'accès, un aperçu le cas "
"échéant et des propriétés liées à l'application dans le cas des programmes."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "For a script the command is the path to the script."
msgid ""
"For a logout script, the command is the path to the script and can not be "
"modified."
msgstr "Pour un script, la commande est l'emplacement vers le script."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Enlever"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
