msgid ""
"This button is only shown when you hover the item with the mouse pointer. "
"Pressing the <guibutton>&minus;</guibutton> button will immediately remove "
"the Desktop file for the program or the script or symbolic link in the "
"<filename class=\"directory\">Autostart</filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"Enlèvera immédiatement le fichier Desktop pour les programmes, le script ou "
"le lien symbolique du dossier <filename class=\"directory\">Autostart</"
